            <abstract>
                <p>The type of this qǝne poem is indicated as <foreign xml:lang="gez">ʿǝṭāna mogar</foreign> 
                    performed in the melodic mode <term key="GeezMode">gǝʿz</term>. However, this type has 
                    seven verses according to <bibl><ptr target="bm:Guidi1900Qene"/><citedRange unit="page">4-5</citedRange></bibl>, 
                    whereas the poem has eight verses, like a<term key="Mawaddes">mawaddǝs</term> qǝne.</p>
